title: We’ve found your next apartment, and it’s amazing!
posting_body: ['Decker Place Apartments', 'Property Address', '3500 Decker Dr., ,', 'Baytown, TX, 77520', '<URL>', 'The search is over!', 'We’ve got a charming 682 Sq.', 'Ft. square foot apartment with your name on it.', 'Come check out our great community and tour your new home.', 'Rents for 1 bed, 1 bath units are as low as $849.00 a month.', 'Floor Plan Details', 'Name: A (1x1)', '1 Bedrooms / 1 Bathrooms', '682 Sq.', 'Ft.', '$849.00 - $899.00', 'Community Amenities', 'Resident BBQ Area', 'On Metro Bus Route', 'Outdoor Seating Areas', 'New LED Lighting', 'Picnic Tables', 'Outdoor Patio Area', 'Beautiful Courtyards', 'Laundry Facility', 'Grills', 'Pet Friendly', 'Deposit Free', 'All Bills Paid', 'Pet Policy', 'Pets may be accepted with a 50-pound limit (maximum of two pets per apartment).', ' Non-refundable pet fee of $300 is required per pet.', ' Certain breeds may be restricted, please contact the leasing office for more details.', ' We comply with all applicable laws regarding Assistance Animals.', 'Office Hours', 'Monday - Friday 8:30 A.M. - 5:30 P.M.', 'ADA ACCESSIBLE', 'EQUAL HOUSING OPPORTUNITY']
